Class FinancialDataGenerator

java.lang.Object
api.mpba.rastvdmy.service.utils.FinancialDataGenerator
Direct Known Subclasses:
AuthServiceImpl, BankAccountServiceImpl, BankIdentityServiceImpl, CardServiceImpl, UserProfileServiceImpl
@Component public class FinancialDataGenerator extends Object
A utility class for generating various financial data, such as bank numbers, IBANs, CVVs, and more.
